author: COMSOL
description: Two analyses show the properties of a Pratt truss bridge: a static stress and deflection analysis of gravitational loads combined with loads representing trucks on the bridge; and an eigenfrequency analysis. The model combines 3D Euler beam elements for the frame structure and shell elements representing the road.
